nodes.text: Adive owner was a male criminal who operated in a dive located in the Coruscant underlevels. During the Clone Wars, he worked as a middleman and hired bounty hunter Aurra Sing to assassinate Ambassador Yong Dolor. However, the assassination attempt was foiled by the intervention of Jedi Master Jyl Somtay. Following this event, the Jedi got a lead on the dive owner as he had previously been arrested for selling the poison that was found on Sing's ryyk blade. Disguised as Sing, Somtay convinced the dive owner to meet with his client in his office. Yong Dolor's assistant, Lorn, was then exposed as the instigator of the assassination attempt. Revealing her true identity, Somtay arrested both Lorn and the dive owner.
